Package: snvtyping
Title: Genomic Context of SNVs From VCF File
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alessandro", "Pandolfi",
    email = "alessandro.pandolfi@protonmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    This package can analyze VCF files containing SNV mutations and convert them
    in a readable Data Frame.
    The main feature is to get the genomic context of all Single Nucleotide 
    Variants mutations in a VCF file; it can also classify and plot them.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
